  <span id="freeText16786420390068427411" style="display:none">This vine of desire winds through family, secrets, friendship, romantic love, betrayal, and grief. This wonderfully and powerfully told story with its companion novel, <i>Sister of My Heart</i> is a heart wrenching and uplifting story of the sisterhood of two women who win and lose in unexpected ways. Divakaruni is one of our country's best story tellers with a poetic voice and deep compassion that transcend culture and geography.</span>
