<div id="review_2037854468" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2037854468" />
    <a title="Anupama Sarkar" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/30537625-anupama-sarkar"><img alt="Anupama Sarkar" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/f_50x66-6a03a5c12233c941481992b82eea8d23.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2037854468?book_show_action=true">Jun 23, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Anupama Sarkar" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Anupama Sarkar" href="/user/show/30537625-anupama-sarkar">Anupama Sarkar</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2037854468" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14867929450912106915">Brilliant storyline, excellent narration and real life characters. This is the best book by Chitra Divakaruni I have read so far.<br/><br/>She is undoubtedly a very talented story writer. But here what I loved even more was the diversity of literary techniques she employed. Letters, dreams, assignments, the alternate voice of prominent characters. You name it and she has used it in this novel. A novel par excellence. Highly recommended. My rating 4.5</span>

          </span>
        </div>


